# 🛍️ Ecommerce Sales Dashboard (Power BI Project)

This project analyzes ecommerce sales using Power BI.  
It covers metrics like:
- Total Sales, Profit, AOV, Quantity
- Sales by State, Customer, Category, Sub-category
- Monthly Profit Trends
- Payment Mode Insights

📊 Dashboard Preview:
![Dashboard Screenshot](Capture.PNG)

## 📁 Datasets
- `Orders.csv` – Contains order-level sales data
- `Details.csv` – Includes item details and category info

## 🛠️ Tools Used
- Power BI
- DAX (for custom calculations)
- Data Cleaning and Transformation

## 🌸 Background
Soft pink theme to create a calm and elegant vibe while analyzing 💗

